(4. HOW TO FILE A WARRANTY CLAIM) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.1 Before You File) Tj
T*
(Gather the following:) Tj
T*
(- Your order number) Tj
T*
(- Photos or a short video demonstrating the defect or issue) Tj
T*
(- A description of when and how the issue first appeared) Tj
T*
(- The product's model number or serial number \(usually on the product or packaging\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.2 Filing a Claim Online) Tj
T*
(1. Log into your account and go to Order History) Tj
T*
(2. Select the order containing the product) Tj
T*
(3. Click "File Warranty Claim") Tj
T*
(4. Describe the issue, upload photos/video, and submit) Tj
T*
(5. You will receive a case number and a response within 2 business days) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
